divs: Sighting DetailsOn Memorial Day 2013 I wanted to confirm whether my gym was opened. The result of my search produced amazing alien craft surrounded by approximately 3-5 force fields surrounding the craft... Also in the space and direction it was heading had an unusual light and dimentional properties.... TRUST ME. THIS IS THE REAL THING.
Summary: While looking up an address online, I panned upward and notice the craft. Additionally for good measure I also searched several addresses blocks 5-10 away from intitial sighting, and confirmed the craft as real. Also force fields were emitted from craft.
